                            <TextBlock x:Name="SoundLinkSummaryLabel" Text="Bass 42 + Vocal 52 + Treble 46 → Cân bằng → EQ nhẹ" Foreground="#17140F" FontSize="13" FontWeight="Black" TextWrapping="Wrap" />
